query:
SELECT id, strategy_symbol, status, is_test, ip_address, timestamp,
       SUBSTRING(payload, 1, 200) as payload_preview
FROM webhook_logs 
WHERE DATE(timestamp) = CURDATE()
ORDER BY timestamp DESC
LIMIT 30;
